\n\nAdded:\n\n- `tests/src/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor_2.13/2.6.21/src/test/scala/com_typesafe_akka/akka_actor_2_13/ReflectTest.scala`\n\nThe new tests exercise Akka public APIs that route through `akka.util.Reflect`:\n\n- Public no-arg actor constructor via `Props(classOf[PublicNoArgActor])`\n- Private no-arg actor constructor to cover `setAccessible(true)` fallback\n- Constructor-argument actor creation to cover constructor lookup and reflective invocation with args\n- ActorSystem creation with a temporarily null context class loader to exercise the `findClassLoader` fallback path where available\n\nI did not run tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b9ba8cec2e898810169fb12ea0ca481918ff473c304aa99ef\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 683, "output": 831, "cacheRead": 25088, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26602, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778062046719, "responseId": "resp_0b9ba8cec2e898810169fb12df2e5481919135c68dc4938e35"}}
